    <div id="comment_41382575">
        <header data-points="1" data-reason="Normal">
            <h3 class="comment-title" data-subject="Re:Spoofing the MAC address?"><i class="com-toggle fa fa-caret-down"></i>Re:Spoofing the MAC address?<span> (1)</span></h3>
            <h4 class="avatar-tiny"><a href="//beta.slashdot.org/~Bob9113" class="author" title="author name and user ID">Bob9113 (14996) </a> | about 2 years ago | <a href="//beta.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=3127217&cid=41382575">(#41382575)</a></h4>
