            <h3 class="comment-title" data-subject="Re:So what?"><i class="com-toggle fa fa-caret-down"></i>Re:So what?<span> (3, Informative)</span></h3>
            <h4 class="avatar-tiny"><span class="author" title="author name and user ID">Anonymous Coward</span> | about 2 years ago | <a href="//beta.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=3127217&cid=41381667">(#41381667)</a></h4>
